Create a new class LeapYear and add main method

-Declare int variable year and check if it is a leap year or not:
 1) A leap year is defined as a year that is divisible by 4 and not divisible by 100
 2) Or, years that are divisible by 400 are also considered leap years.

Ex: year is 2036 -> "2036 is a leap year"
    year is 2025 -> "2036 is not a leap year"
