Create a new class GasMileageCalculator and add main method
https://www.calculator.net/gas-mileage-calculator.html

-Declare int variables currentOdometer, previousOdometer, gallons
    formula: miles per gallon is currentOdometer -  previousOdometer divided by gallons

-Calculate and assign result int mpg (miles per gallon) variable
    if mpg is 40 or more -> Print "Great gas mileage"
    22 or more "Good gas mileage"
    less than that "Poor gas mileage"
