Create a new class Overtime and add main method

hourlyRate = 45, hours = 45, calculate double pay

if hours is more than 40:
    print "Overtime" and
    first 40 hours is regular hourlyRate
    anything over 40 is overtime pay, which is 55 per hour
    Calculate that and assign to pay
else:
    multiply hours by hourlyRate and assign to pay

-print out weekly gross pay
-calculate tax as 25% then print out net pay
